{"tid":354982,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱去完峴港，而家人在胡志明，你問我答。","createTime":"2017-08-11T02:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T16:09:03.000Z","uid":32293,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"561429471dacfd810c7d30a5d276f0bfde6093d0","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"事先聲明，峴港景點基本上淨係去過會安同Hon Market，五行山巴拿山都冇去過，所以你問景點我可能答到嘅唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n胡志明噚日晚機先到（仆街又係Delay），行過下范五老街咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有想去或者就去越南嘅巴絲有嘢想知，我盡答<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇搵過Emma，唔知喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9436b3ada4e22a5116173c065052b8c08422970","tid":354982,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"993b6916e55b7763031677879e6ad6e65f2d5275","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪胡春嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8350949cac0069ddb017c3658a5ce0aea5bde4","tid":354982,"uid":48156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"下個月去。會係會安附近住兩日。你覺得會安有無需要買門票？或者一定要買？"},{"pid":"57f21830439465a74ab98456c0bcc644e8792b71","tid":354982,"uid":41863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"巴打想問下峴港本身有咩玩? 有冇食好西既地方推介呢?<br />\n仲有你係辦落地簽證嗎? USD8+USD25? 入境時等得耐嗎?"},{"pid":"c718ad1a272aec4d62cf36f8f2ea86f866bf9c41","tid":354982,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"叫左幾次雞？<br />\n唔好扮正人君子"},{"pid":"bccbcef4080238fb37159677cd8ce4e51773e64a","tid":354982,"uid":3086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-