-08-12T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"峴港點租私家車？"},{"pid":"7e5998da0fe8f1edd810776a05c3d3acc075a236","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>峴港有無泰國哥種水上活動玩？我玩下浮潛就夠，水靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n有見人玩水上電單車，滑翔傘<br />\n水幾正，浮潛要去另一個島，好似係"},{"pid":"12c6c2331521a9405c8272ad5b4cf3ed2415e205","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>峴港點租私家車？</blockquote><br />\n依個真係唔知，但聽講好多人租電單車，好抵。"},{"pid":"d41bcffee2d1861661c2c7b60421a93b69f42d69","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 講得唔清楚<br />\n機場visa on arrival 係咪24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗係掛，但有凌晨機去峴港咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我搭夜機去到起碼10點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗有機就開啦，唔通叫你瞓住等咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打仲有冇其他餐廳地方推薦<br />\n你有冇去埋會安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要峴港定會胡志明？<br />\n會安有去，晏就真係好撚熱，佢有冷氣嘅鋪頭得幾間，我諗你五點先去就差唔多。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住會安嗰邊但都會去埋峴港<br />\n唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得幾間</blockquote><br />\n你要預咗成個峴港有冷氣嘅地方得酒點，spa，仲有高級餐廳。<br />\n會安啲建築係好古色古香冇變過，咁冇現代嘅冷氣都好正常吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86cdbe25f52937d4902d491feec7d2b85d4e516","tid":354982,"uid":32293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我諗係掛，但有凌晨機去峴港咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我搭夜機去到起碼10點 <img src=\"/as